import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Box } from '@mui/material';
import PhishingIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Phishing';
import LeaderboardIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Leaderboard';
import SetMealIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SetMeal';

function HighlightsSection() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#f7f7f7', paddingY: 8 }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Typography
          variant="h5"
          sx={{
            textAlign: 'center',
            fontWeight: 'bold',
            fontSize: { xs: '1.8rem', md: '2.5rem' },
            color: '#2a5e4f',
            marginBottom: 4,
            fontFamily: 'Poppins, sans-serif',
          }}
        >
          Why Choose Our Fishing App?
        </Typography>
        <Box textAlign="center" mb={2}>
          <PhishingIcon sx={{ color: '#2a5e4f', fontSize: '3rem' }} />
        </Box>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Box textAlign="center">
              <PhishingIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#2a5e4f', marginBottom: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#2a5e4f', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                Trusted Tournaments
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
                Participate in verified online fishing tournaments and win prizes.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Box textAlign="center">
              <LeaderboardIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#2a5e4f', marginBottom: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#2a5e4f', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                Real-Time Scoring
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
                Track your progress with real-time leaderboards.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Box textAlign="center">
              <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#2a5e4f', marginBottom: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#2a5e4f', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                Secure Payments
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
                Safe and reliable payment methods for prize distribution.
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default HighlightsSection;
